OL,3,CEngland batter Ben Duckett guilty of
OL,4,C93mph speeding before cricket match
OL,6,FEngland batter Ben Duckett has been
OL,7,Fconvicted of speeding at 93mph and
OL,8,Ffined #700 by a court, in the same
OL,9,Fweek that he pulled out of the Indian
OL,10,FPremier League in a bid to rescue his
OL,11,Finternational career.
OL,13,FThe 31-year-old, who plays for
OL,14,FNottinghamshire, was convicted by a
OL,15,Fcourt of speeding along the A50 near
OL,16,FStoke in Staffordshire at 93mph.
OL,18,FDuckett was pictured at the wheel of
OL,19,Fhis Land Rover breaking the 70mph
OL,20,Flimit as the vehicle was caught on a
OL,21,Fpolice speed gun on 24 August 2025.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
