OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774976748
OL,3,CEngland batter Ben Duckett guilty of
OL,4,C93mph speeding before cricket match
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to the offence at
OL,7,FCannock Magistrates' Court, and was
OL,8,Fhanded a #700 fine, four penalty
OL,9,Fpoints on his licence, and an order to
OL,10,Falso pay #120 in costs and a #280
OL,11,Fvictim surcharge.
OL,13,FDuckett admitted the speeding offence
OL,14,Fin September after being written to by
OL,15,FStaffordshire Police.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
