PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774976748
OL,3,CEngland batter Ben Duckett guilty of
OL,4,C93mph speeding before cricket match
OL,6,FHe then pleaded guilty through the
OL,7,FSingle Justice Procedure when the
OL,8,Fforce decided to bring a criminal
OL,9,Fprosecution rather than impose an out-
OL,10,Fof-court fine, due to the high speed
OL,11,Fhe had been driving.
OL,13,FHis place as a Test cricket opener for
OL,14,FEngland is in doubt after a nosedive
OL,15,Fin his form over the past year,
OL,16,Ftogether with controversy over a
OL,17,Fdrunken incident during the winter
OL,18,FAshes tour.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
