PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774976748
OL,3,CEngland batter Ben Duckett guilty of
OL,4,C93mph speeding before cricket match
OL,6,FDuckett pulled out of a #200,000 deal
OL,7,Flast week to play for the Delhi
OL,8,FCapitals in the IPL, saying he wanted
OL,9,Fto focus on county cricket and
OL,10,Fsecuring his spot in the Test side
OL,11,Fahead of this summer's series against
OL,12,FNew Zealand.
OL,14,FHe also issued an apology for past
OL,15,Funprofessionalism, particularly an
OL,16,Fincident when he was filmed drunk on a
OL,17,Fnight out in Noosa, Australia, midway
OL,18,Fthrough the Ashes.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
