PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774976748
OL,3,CEngland batter Ben Duckett guilty of
OL,4,C93mph speeding before cricket match
OL,6,FAs a rising star in 2015, he was
OL,7,Fprosecuted for drink-driving after
OL,8,Fcrashing his car into a ditch in
OL,9,FNorthamptonshire, leading to a 12-
OL,10,Fmonth road ban.
OL,12,FDuckett was first selected for
OL,13,FEngland's Test side in 2016, but ran
OL,14,Finto controversy the following year
OL,15,Fwhen he reportedly poured a drink over
OL,16,Fbowler James Anderson's head during a
OL,17,Fnight out.
OL,19,FHe became a key player as an opener
OL,20,Ffor England from 2022, adapting well
OL,21,Fto the team's "Bazball" style of play.
OL,26,@}D@OOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
