OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774976748
OL,3,CEngland batter Ben Duckett guilty of
OL,4,C93mph speeding before cricket match
OL,6,FHowever, Duckett himself has
OL,7,Facknowledged the "ridiculously big
OL,8,Fdip" in his form over the last year,
OL,9,Fwhile the incident in Noosa ` during
OL,10,Fthe Ashes tour ` placed him again at
OL,11,Fthe centre of a drunken night out
OL,12,Fcontroversy.
OL,14,F"I am sorry for that incident, it was
OL,15,Fnot professional and shouldn't have
OL,16,Fhappened", he told the Telegraph last
OL,17,Fweek.
OL,19,F"There is no hiding away from it."
