OL,3,CEngland batter Ben Duckett guilty of
OL,4,C93mph speeding before cricket match
OL,6,FDuckett's speeding prosecution was
OL,7,Fdealt with behind closed doors last
OL,8,FFriday without a formal court hearing.
OL,10,FThe cricketer entered his guilty plea
OL,11,Fonline and will now be written to with
OL,12,Finstructions for settling the #1,100
OL,13,Fcourt bill.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
